query:
SELECT id, auditTypeId, auditDate, status, assignedAuditorId, serviceUserId, locationId
FROM auditInstances 
WHERE locationId = 30001 
  AND auditDate >= '2025-10-01' 
  AND auditDate <= '2025-12-31'
ORDER BY auditDate;
